These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Food: nectarine, orange
City: prague, hamburg
1. City:prague is in an even position##4
2. City:hamburg == Food:orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | orange | nectarine |
| City     | hamburg    | prague   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Flower: marigold, aconite
House: colonial, craftsman
1. House:colonial is in an odd position##4
2. Flower:aconite is on the left of Flower:marigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | aconite | marigold        |
| House      | colonial  | craftsman |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
City: rome, hannover
Movie-Genre: action, comedy
1. Movie-Genre:action is in an odd position##4
2. City:hannover is on the left of City:rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| City   | hannover    | rome |
| Movie-Genre   | action | comedy |

