Flower: aconite, marigold
1. Pet:bird is on the right of Pet:goat##1
2. Flower:marigold is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | goat      | bird |
| Flower       | aconite | marigold    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
