.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
Birthday: november, august
House: tower, cottage
1. House:cottage == Birthday:august##1
2. House:tower is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Birthday          | august | november |
| House   | cottage | tower   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
Transport: jet-ski, subway
House: modern, townhouse
1. Transport:subway is in an odd position##4
2. House:modern is on the left or right of Transport:jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Transport   | subway | jet-ski   |
| House         | modern | townhouse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-12::.
